<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#06080d;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0}
    .wrap{max-width:520px;margin:40px auto;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
    .header{padding:24px 30px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111827,#162032);border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b}
    .logo{font-size:19px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b}
    .body{padding:30px}
    h2{font-size:19px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 10px}
    p{color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 12px}
    .prod-card{background:#162032;border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3);border-radius:10px;padding:18px;margin:20px 0}
    .prod-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#e2e8f0;margin-bottom:6px}
    .prod-price{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b}
    .prod-status{display:inline-block;background:rgba(16,185,129,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3);color:#10b981;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;margin-top:8px}
    .tips{margin:16px 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
    .tip{font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px}
    .cta{display:block;background:#f59e0b;color:#000;text-align:center;padding:13px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;margin:20px 0}
    .footer{padding:16px 30px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#475569}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="header"><div class="logo">☀️ Solar Maket</div></div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Your Product is Live! 🎉</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}}, your product listing has been reviewed and approved. It is now live on Solar Maket and visible to thousands of buyers.</p>

      <div class="prod-card">
        <div class="prod-name">{{product.name}}</div>
        <div class="prod-price">₦{{product.price}}</div>
        <div class="prod-status">✓ LIVE</div>
      </div>

      <p><strong style="color:#e2e8f0">Tips to increase visibility:</strong></p>
      <div class="tips">
        <div class="tip"><span>📸</span><span>Add high-quality photos from multiple angles</span></div>
        <div class="tip"><span>📋</span><span>Fill in all technical specifications — buyers filter by them</span></div>
        <div class="tip"><span>💰</span><span>Competitive pricing gets more enquiries</span></div>
        <div class="tip"><span>⚡</span><span>Our AI Advisor recommends products matching buyers' system needs</span></div>
      </div>

      <a href="{{product.url}}" class="cta">View Your Live Listing →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">© {{year}} Solar Maket Nigeria Ltd. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
